"Description for table: GraphAccount"
type GraphAccount @entity {
  "Unique identifier for the account"
  id: ID!
  "List of names associated with the account, derived from the graphAccount field"
  names: [GraphAccountName!]! @derivedFrom(field: "graphAccount")
  "The default name for the account"
  defaultName: GraphAccountName
  "Timestamp of when the account was created"
  createdAt: Int!
  "The default display name for the account"
  defaultDisplayName: String
  "Metadata associated with the account"
  metadata: GraphAccountMeta
  "Accounts operated by this account, derived from the operators field"
  operatorOf: [GraphAccount!]! @derivedFrom(field: "operators")
  "List of accounts that operate this account"
  operators: [GraphAccount!]!
  "Current balance of the account"
  balance: BigInt!
  "Balance received from L1 signalling"
  balanceReceivedFromL1Signalling: BigInt!
  "Balance received from L1 delegation"
  balanceReceivedFromL1Delegation: BigInt!
  "Approval amount for curation"
  curationApproval: BigInt!
  "Approval amount for staking"
  stakingApproval: BigInt!
  "Approval amount for GNS"
  gnsApproval: BigInt!
  "Subgraphs owned by the account, derived from the owner field"
  subgraphs: [Subgraph!]! @derivedFrom(field: "owner")
  "Timestamp of when the developer was created"
  developerCreatedAt: Int
  "Fees from subgraph queries"
  subgraphQueryFees: BigInt!
  "Disputes created by the account, derived from the fisherman field"
  createdDisputes: [Dispute!]! @derivedFrom(field: "fisherman")
  "Disputes against the account, derived from the indexer field"
  disputesAgainst: [Dispute!]! @derivedFrom(field: "indexer")
  "Curator associated with the account"
  curator: Curator
  "Indexer associated with the account"
  indexer: Indexer
  "Delegator associated with the account"
  delegator: Delegator
  "Transactions related to name signalling, derived from the signer field"
  nameSignalTransactions: [NameSignalTransaction!]! @derivedFrom(field: "signer")
  "Transactions for bridge withdrawals, derived from the signer field"
  bridgeWithdrawalTransactions: [BridgeWithdrawalTransaction!]! @derivedFrom(field: "signer")
  "Transactions for bridge deposits, derived from the signer field"
  bridgeDepositTransactions: [BridgeDepositTransaction!]! @derivedFrom(field: "signer")
  "Wallets with token locks associated with the account"
  tokenLockWallets: [TokenLockWallet!]!
}

"Description for table: GraphAccountMeta"
type GraphAccountMeta @entity(immutable: true) {
  "Unique identifier for the GraphAccountMeta entry."
  id: ID!

  graphAccount: GraphAccount @derivedFrom(field: "metadata")
  "List of GraphAccounts associated with this metadata."
  graphAccounts: [GraphAccount!]! @derivedFrom(field: "metadata")
  "Indicates whether the account is an organization."
  isOrganization: Boolean
  "URL of the code repository associated with the account."
  codeRepository: String
  "Textual description of the account."
  description: String
  "URL of the image associated with the account."
  image: String
  "Website URL of the account."
  website: String
  "Display name of the account."
  displayName: String
}

"Description for table: GraphAccountName"
type GraphAccountName @entity {
  "Unique identifier for the GraphAccountName entity."

}

"Description for enum type: NameSystem"
enum NameSystem {
  "Ethereum Name Service"
  ENS
}

"Description for table: Subgraph"
type Subgraph @entity {

  "Block number when the transfer to Layer 2 started."
  startedTransferToL2AtBlockNumber: BigInt
  "Transaction ID when the transfer to Layer 2 started."
  startedTransferToL2AtTx: String

  transferredToL2: Boolean!

  transferredToL2At: BigInt
  "Block number when the subgraph was transferred to Layer 2."
  transferredToL2AtBlockNumber: BigInt

  transferredToL2AtTx: String
  "Amount of signalled tokens sent to Layer 2."
  signalledTokensSentToL2: BigInt!
  "Amount of signalled tokens received on Layer 2."
  signalledTokensReceivedOnL2: BigInt!
  "Identifier of the subgraph on Layer 2."
  idOnL2: String
  "Identifier of the subgraph on Layer 1."
  idOnL1: String
  "NFT identifier associated with the subgraph."
  nftID: String
  "Previous identifier of the subgraph."
  oldID: String
  "Address of the creator of the subgraph."
  creatorAddress: Bytes
  "Number associated with the subgraph."
  subgraphNumber: BigInt
  "Indicates if the subgraph is in the process of initializing."
  initializing: Boolean!
  "Version of the entity schema."
  entityVersion: Int!
  "Linked subgraph entity."
  linkedEntity: Subgraph
  "Total amount of tokens signalled."
  signalledTokens: BigInt!
  "Total amount of tokens unsignalled."
  unsignalledTokens: BigInt!
  "Current amount of tokens signalled."
  currentSignalledTokens: BigInt!
  "Amount of name signal tokens."
  nameSignalAmount: BigInt!
  "Total signal amount."
  signalAmount: BigInt!
  "Reserve ratio for the subgraph."
  reserveRatio: Int!
  "Amount of tokens that can be withdrawn."
  withdrawableTokens: BigInt!
  "Total amount of tokens withdrawn."
  withdrawnTokens: BigInt!
  "List of name signals, derived from the subgraph field."
  nameSignals: [NameSignal!]! @derivedFrom(field: "subgraph")
  "Count of name signals."
  nameSignalCount: Int!
  "Hash of the metadata."
  metadataHash: Bytes
  "Metadata associated with the subgraph."
  metadata: SubgraphMeta
  "Relation entity for the current version of the subgraph."
  currentVersionRelationEntity: CurrentSubgraphDeploymentRelation
}

"Description for table: SubgraphMeta"
type SubgraphMeta @entity(immutable: true) {
